<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖面开始冒泡，湖水翻滚着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波浪拍打着湖岸。一个巨人冒出水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西向下看去， “我变大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西小心走在市区的大楼之间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心点。”她告诉自己，“你不想踩到任何人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到一只青蛙黏在美罗城银行的大楼上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只青蛙黏糊恶心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是现在罗西比它大多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西深深吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我可以的。我能拿青蛙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她闭着眼睛向青蛙伸出手去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西感觉它黏黏的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃!” 她喊道，手赶紧缩回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西重新伸出手去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次她小心地从大楼上捡起那个黏糊糊的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西手里拿着青蛙，飞回公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把青蛙扔进紫色的湖水里。扑通！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也不是很难。”罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞回美罗城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一只接一只找出了所有的青蛙，并把它们都丢进湖里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西说，“真高兴都干完了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过这些青蛙还是太大了，我也是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到底是什么东西把我们变大的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西想了想，低头看向紫色的湖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”她说，“是那块陨石。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走进湖里，用双手在水下东摸西摸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就找到了陨石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把它从水里拿出来以后，湖水马上退去了紫色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把陨石抛向天空，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那块紫色的石头划过天空，在远离地球的太空消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西又开始觉得怪怪的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在缩小！”罗西想，“青蛙也在缩小。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的朋友们从树林里走出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们站在湖边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很想知道罗西去哪儿了。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她可能回家了吧。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她真的很害怕巨型青蛙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉看到一只青蛙跳出水面，她伸出手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”她说，“这里还有一只青蛙，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只正常大小的青蛙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家好！”她说，“我回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨型青蛙很吓人，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着玛拉。“哇！我能抓一下那只青蛙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你害怕青蛙呢。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把青蛙递给罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不怕了。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着罗西，但是他什么也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>